{"tid":2145800,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"駱惠寧：特朗普收皮啦 你咸家產都未開到我年啊傻閪 你係到谷撚住都冇撚用你啖氣忍到下世啦柒頭","createTime":"2020-08-08T08:21:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T15:09:01.000Z","uid":38189,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8d12cda40b9db55fa1eb5a76fdea6b5686f286ba","tid":2145800,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T08:21:03.000Z","msg":"特狗收皮啦 你咸家產都未開到我年啊傻閪<br />\n你係到谷撚住都冇撚用你啖氣忍到下世啦柒頭<br />\n我笠撚硬水 你今世都打唔撚到我架啦<br />\n你繼續吠啦傻閪<br />\n屌你老母制埋裁<br />\n比人笑都好過比你打到變豬頭啦傻閪<br />\n突然約隻抽都知你兩手準備 日操夜操想搵我做沙包 你都戇撚鳩<br />\n正所謂 阿婆跑得快 一定有古怪<br />\n150%肯撚定特狗有練開武嘅<br />\n咁突然搵我隻抽 你當我傻？屌你老味<br />\n比你笑我笠水 你叻囉<br />\n雖然笠水啫 你當我傻架？叫個跑開步從來唔打拳出黎比你打鑊金 你老母生撚左你個腦未 屌你老母"},{"pid":"22ae7e28efcb83f1159d4648562d3e34fd6b3e37","tid":2145800,"uid":199081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T08:21:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a17de5a7a2c3a87a933f04106d8c9b7719723109","tid":2145800,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T08:25:54.000Z","msg":"米抽拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c181b629a02918f1f078593835928b0fb0647030","tid":2145800,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a17de5a7a2c3a87a933f04106d8c9b7719723109","tid":2145800,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T08:25:54.000Z","msg":"米抽拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T08:27:19.000Z","msg":"特狗同宇狗一樣得個嬲字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"130d31edb9cfc92db8d8cf1273163d74cb3d13ae","tid":2145800,"uid":175032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T08:31:30.000Z","msg":"笠青=波台駱惠寧<br />\n定駱惠寧=中共笠青？"},{"pid":"04462673ce54375aab67c8e307ddc8a900ecc7bd","tid":2145800,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T08:32:4